<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.7">
<l>vaṇṭamarum malarppuṉṉai varinīḻa laṇimuttam</l>
<l>teṇṭiraikaḷ varattiraṭṭun tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>eṇṭicaiyu meḻucuṭaru mirunilaṉum peruvicumpum</l>
<l>uṇṭumiḻnta perumāṉuk kiḻantēṉe ṉoḷivaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my bright bangles to the great lord who, having eaten</l>
<l>The eight regions, the rising sun, the wide world,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the vast heavens, spit [them] out,</l>
<l>[And] who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram where lovely pearls collect</l>
<l rend="indent">when clear waves come</l>
<l>In the dappled shade of the laurel with blossoms where bees linger.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
